This will be my last post for tonight. 

::Feline::

She took his arm and held it tightly with hers.  She walked with him 
resting her head on his shoulder.   She smiled and purred softly.
"I want to thank you. You have been most kind.  I don't know how to 
repay your kindness to me. But thank you."
She leaned up and kissed his cheek and put her head back on her 
shoulder.
